Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 08-01-2025

At Halal Cruise, your privacy is our priority. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your information when you use our app.

1. Information We Collect
Our app does not require login or collect personal information such as names, emails, or phone numbers.

2. How We Use Your Information
We do not store or process personal data. If you choose to contact us via email, your email will open in your device’s email app, and we will only use your message to respond to your query.

3. Data Security
Since we do not collect or store data, there are no risks of unauthorized access to your information through our app.

4. Third-Party Services
Our app may include links to external websites or third-party services (e.g., for bookings or cruises). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external platforms. Please review their privacy policies.

5. Children’s Privacy
Our app is designed for general audiences and does not knowingly collect any information from children.

6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted here with the updated effective date.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via email at: shammughal811@gmail.com
